description.en:
First target of Dating Token project is: to  launch a p2p transparent and decentralized dating platform .
     Purpose of the project is: creating a payment gateway which use dtng token. 
     DTNG Payment gateway will provide users secure and hidden payment.system, users can be able to send gifts to the matches without giving personal information.
